Articles.Content:
ckan dies every time i try to load one of my installs of ksp.

- open ckan

- select ksp 1.6.1

-

- click dismiss.

- command prompt thing lingers for a bit but then disappears.

this only happens with my ksp version 1.6.1

mods:
